Hydras looked up at the ship. It had to go down. He flew form his present 
battle and pulled out his two swords. His hands seemed to melt or make the 
metal softer. He then cut through a hole big enough to cut through. He looked 
at his hands with three magnet bombs. He placed the three around the cargo 
bay. He flew out and they would explode soon after. (its meant to do dmaage 
not destory it they are small to medium explosion bombs.)
